@startuml
skinparam BackgroundColor transparent

card "Disaster Risk\n(Риск бедствий, R_c)" as Risk #lightgray

card "Hazard\n(Опасность, H)" as Hazard #ffcccc
card "Exposure\n(Досягаемость, E)" as Exposure #ccccff
card "Vulnerability\n(Уязвимость, V)" as Vulnerability #ccffcc

card "Sensitivity\n(Чувствительность, S)" as Sensitivity #white
card "Adaptability\n(Адаптивность, A)" as Adaptability #white

Hazard --> Risk
Exposure --> Risk
Vulnerability --> Risk

Sensitivity --> Vulnerability
Adaptability --> Vulnerability

note bottom of Risk
  Риск возникает только при
  пересечении H, E и V
end note
@enduml